title: Indian Students In Ukraine's Sumy Say Evacuation On Hold Again - NDTV
content: Indian Students In Ukraine's Sumy Say Evacuation On Hold Again  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: The evacuation of around 700 Indian students stranded in battle-torn Ukraine's Sumy was put on hold again today as Ukraine vetoed the Russian idea of a humanitarian corridor from three of its cities to Russia and Belarus, calling it an "unethical".
